[5] Chile (Nuble province, BioBio region)
Date: Wed 4 Apr 2012
Source: La Discusion [in Spanish, trans & summ. Mod.TY, edited]
http://www.diarioladiscusion.cl/index.php/noticias/100-salud1651607246/10165-confirman-contagio-de-hanta-en-estudiante


After a student was admitted this past Friday [30 Mar 2012] to the Clinica Las Condes in Santiago with a preliminary diagnosis of hantavirus infection, yesterday [3 Apr 2012], the Institute of Public Health confirmed the result as positive, together with another 2 people in the capital.

As a result, the positive reports have increased to 4 [cases] in the Nuble province [BioBio region].

