[6] Chile (Santiago and Chillan, BioBio region)
Date: Tue 3 Apr 2012
Source: Cooperativa [in Spanish, trans. & summ. Mod.TY, edited]
http://www.cooperativa.cl/isp-confirmo-dos-nuevos-casos-de-virus-hanta-en-el-pais/prontus_nots/2012-04-03/161144.html


The Institute of Public Health confirmed 2 new hantavirus infection cases in the country. The 1st of these is a 47-year-old woman in serious condition in the clinic of the Universidad Catolica de San Carlos de Apoquindo.

Also, there is a 27-year-old man who was hospitalized in the Clinica Las Amapolas in Chillan who also was diagnosed as a serious case.

